reviewText: I bought this movie because William Boyd aka Hopalong Cassidy was in it.  It is an enjoyable movie which I think anyone would like.

As usual William Boyd is the finest of actors which was the reason for my purchase of this dvd in the first place.  I've  been one of his greatest fans since childhood.  The other actors were good, so no problem there.  Could only give it three stars because the story was less than what I expected.
